  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6799.16 sitting just below the massive 6800 gamma wall (86.3B) in PIN regime, dealers are likely selling into any strength as spot approaches this critical level. The positive gamma fortress from 6790-6810 creates a powerful mean-reversion zone where dealers will aggressively hedge against directional moves, with the recent wall break event suggesting we just tested and likely bounced off key support. Watch 6800 as the primary resistance where dealer selling intensifies, while 6780 flip strike acts as the regime boundary - a break below shifts dealers to buying mode.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect price to get pinned between 6790-6800 with limited breakout potential.",
